<div class="navbar">
<span id="thisPage"><%= link_to "Home", root_path, id: "selected" %></span>
<%= link_to "All Products", products_path %>
</div>

<h1>Mario's Specialty Food Products</h1>

<h2>About Mario's</h2>
<p>Mario's is probably the newest food fad. You could learn more about us if you wanted to, but there really isn't that much to us. I would recommend spending your time doing something more productive. Also you should invest in medium risk mutual funds.</p>

<% if @products.any? %>
  <h2>Mario's Three Newest Creations</h2>
  <ul>
    <% @products.each do |product| %>
    <div class="productTop">
      <li class="product"><%= link_to product.name, product_path(product.id), class: 'products' %></li>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </ul>
  <h2>Mario's Most Reviewed Product</h2>
  <p class="product"><%= link_to @most_reviewed_product.first.name, product_path(@most_reviewed_product.first.id), class: 'products' %></p>
<% else %>
  <p>Mario's is so popular that it sold out of everything and you were too slow get get anything. Try being faster next time.</p>
<% end %>
